Provenance / permission
----------------------

This repository contains a modified version of the "billy" basis-set and geometry
optimisation script originally developed by Mike Towler.

The original author granted explicit permission (email dated 13 Nov 2025) for
unrestricted use, modification, and redistribution, with no acknowledgement
required.

This repository adds CRYSTAL23-first configuration and additional functionality
used in the associated publication by Wynand Dednam. See README.md for details.
